Package: rmorielite
Type: Package
Title: Polite Retrieval of Canadian Carceral and Police-Oversight Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person(
    given = "Vansh Singh",
    family = "Ruhela",
    email = "vsruhela@proton.me",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0004-1750-3592")
  )
 )
Maintainer: Vansh Singh Ruhela <vsruhela@proton.me>
Description: Polite-by-default fetching, manifest-aware caching, and
  schema-validated ingestion for two openly-published Canadian
  administrative datasets: the Ontario Offender Tracking Information
  System (OTIS) restrictive-confinement detailed dataset, and federal
  Structured Intervention Unit (SIU) reports. Scoped narrowly to data
  retrieval and extraction. The full multi-domain rmorie toolkit
  (causal inference, MRM framework, statistical physics, signal
  processing, cryptography) lives upstream at
  <https://github.com/rootcoder007/rmorie>.
